reviewText: There are 12 DVD's in this series.  The eleventh in the series is a bit disappointing.  It shows the expected flashing and total nudity.  Why is this disappointing?  It doesn't go as far as the others.  I'd give it four stars.  The way to think about the others is that the titles really mean something.  In particular, I'm referring to "Beyond."  It is remarkable how far some girls will go in full view of dozens of people.  The most explicit scenes, however, were filmed in doors; in a hotel corridor, an indoor parking lot, elsewhere.  Try one of the eleven (1-10, 12).  I give them five stars.

I emailed this seller several times and never got any reply back.  I payed right away and never received any DVD's.  No communication whatsoever.  This seller will take your money and would never recommend them to anyone.  NEVER BUY FROM THIS PERSON.
I must have walked into something and got sh_t on my shoe - oh no my mistake it's just a ggw dvd.
